Add an option in the edit menu to change the font

TEXTAREA -> txtEditor -> getCharacters -> keytyped
LABEL    -> lblDisplay
OPEN     ->  btnOpen -> onOpen  <--------  Open Text File
SAVE     ->  btnSave -> onSave  <--------  Save Text File
EDIT     ->  btnEdit -> onEdit              Close -> onExit
LOCK     ->  btnLock -> onLock